OL,3,CMoment drink-driver causes head-on
OL,4,Ccollision with children in car
OL,6,FPolice release footage of the head-on
OL,7,Fcollision
OL,9,FA Malmesbury man who lost control of
OL,10,Fhis vehicle whilst under the influence
OL,11,Fof alcohol has been given a driving
OL,12,Fban.
OL,14,FOn 25 March last year, Simon Wright,
OL,15,Fof Parklands in Malmesbury, was
OL,16,Fdriving an Audi RS4 with a front seat
OL,17,Fpassenger and children in the vehicle
OL,18,Fwhen the crash happened.
OL,20,FThe 43-year-old was driving from
OL,21,FMalmesbury to Little Somerford.
