OL,4,Ccollision with children in car
OL,6,FHe was seen to exit Priory roundabout
OL,7,Fat such speed having overtaken two
OL,8,Fvehicles, he lost control of the car
OL,9,Fand skidded into the face of oncoming
OL,10,Ftraffic, colliding with another
OL,11,Fvehicle.
OL,13,FEmergency services attended the scene
OL,14,Fand Wright failed a breath test.
OL,16,FHe sustained a number of injuries
OL,17,Fwhilst it is believed his front seat
OL,18,Fpassenger was also injured. The
OL,19,Fchildren were treated for shock but
OL,20,Ffortunately were not injured.
