OL,6,FThe driver and the passenger of the
OL,7,Fsecond vehicle were admitted to
OL,8,Fhospital but not seriously injured.
OL,10,FWright appeared at Swindon Crown Court
OL,11,Fon 26 July and pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Fdriving dangerously and drink driving.
OL,14,FHe was given a two year driving
OL,15,Fdisqualification, an 18 month
OL,16,Fsuspended prison sentence and ordered
OL,17,Fto carry out 200 hours of unpaid work.
OL,18,FHe must also pay #2,000 compensation
OL,19,Fand a #187 surcharge.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
