OL,6,FPC Luke Hobbs, from the Roads Policing
OL,7,FUnit, said: "This standard of driving,
OL,8,Fespecially whilst under the influence
OL,9,Fof alcohol, is totally unacceptable on
OL,10,Four roads and poses a significant
OL,11,Fdanger to other road users.
OL,13,F"The fact that there were young
OL,14,Fchildren also in the vehicle at the
OL,15,Ftime does not bear thinking about.
