OL,4,Ccollision with children in car
OL,6,F"We all know alcohol can give you a
OL,7,Ffalse sense of confidence and
OL,8,Funfortunately all too often we see
OL,9,Fdrivers getting behind the wheel of a
OL,10,Fcar having consumed alcohol under the
OL,11,Fimpression they are invincible. It
OL,12,Fshould not take a serious collision
OL,13,Flike this to understand the serious
OL,14,Fconsequences of your actions if you
OL,15,Fare one of these people.
OL,17,F"I am pleased that as a result of his
OL,18,Fselfish and mindless actions, Wright
OL,19,Fhas been banned from our roads."
